            "title_max_width_desktop": 235,
            "description": "<p>LifeSync Advanced Manufacturing is purpose-built for the precision, scale, and regulatory discipline medical device OEMs demand. Our model combines embedded engineering collaboration with modular automation and integrated operations to deliver predictable outcomes from prototype through production. </p><p></p><p> </p>",
