            "title_max_width_desktop": 0,
            "description": "<p>One team. One goal. Your success. LifeSync integrates early into your engineering and R&D processes—partnering as an extension of your team, not a downstream assembler. From requirements definition and prototyping through regulatory approval and full production, LifeSync reduces development risk, shortens time to market, and improves production readiness. Quality isn't an inspection step for at the end; it’s engineered from the start. </p>",
