            "title_max_width_desktop": 235,
            "description": "<p>LifeSync is the industry proven leader in automated SpO2 & ECG manufacturing. Our global, ISO-certified operations leverage modular, scalable automation to deliver cost efficiency and consistent quality, optimized for complex, high mix-low volume environments. Our automation expertise is engineered into the design process from the outset, enabling rapid transition from prototype to production and high First Pass Yield (FPY) with excellence in predictable supply, yield, and cost control.</p>",
